graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.21+<br/>Required]
    KubeRay -->|operator framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime 0.16.3<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Optional]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano 1.6.0+<br/>Optional]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS fault tolerance| Redis[External Redis 6.0+<br/>Optional]

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional] -->|scrapes metrics| KubeRay
    Prometheus -->|scrapes cluster metrics| RayCluster

    %% Internal RHOAI/ODH Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|external access| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>route.openshift.io/v1]
    KubeRay -.->|mTLS integration| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Istio<br/>Optional]
    MonitoringStack[RHOAI Monitoring Stack] -->|platform metrics| Prometheus

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| KubeRay
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|cluster creation| KubeRay
    Notebooks[Notebook Environments] -->|user clusters| KubeRay

    %% Managed Resources
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| RayCluster[Ray Cluster<br/>Head + Workers]
    RayCluster -->|stores data| Storage[S3/GCS/Azure Blob<br/>External]
    RayCluster -->|pulls images| Registry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io/gcr.io]

    %% Custom Resources
    Users[Data Scientists] -->|creates| CRDs
    CRDs[RayCluster CR<br/>RayJob CR<br/>RayService CR]
    CRDs -->|watched by| KubeRay

